{"tid":1496062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【共度時艱】零售管理協會籲商舖業主減租五成","createTime":"2019-08-22T10:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:38:20.000Z","uid":33307,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d2bcbd728bef3fd5aeee19426bf65b321a8163","tid":1496062,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"就近期零售市道急速下滑，協會向商舖業主作出呼籲，共度時艱。香港零售管理協會會員反映生意額由6月開始急轉直下，銷售額的跌幅已由單位數擴大至雙位數。大部分零售商於8月初至今的銷售額更大幅跌逾五成。<br />\n<br />\n零售商在營運成本高昂及收入銳減的情況下，承受龐大的現金流壓力。若情況持續惡化，預料不少零售商或會裁員甚至結業。 <br />\n<br />\n在此關鍵時刻，協會已向全港商舖業主發信呼籲，向租戶減租五成，為期6個月，共度時艱。 <br />\n<br />\n業界表示政府日前公布的措施未能給予針對性的幫助。協會呼籲政府向零售商提供即時紓困方案，例如財務資助及差餉寬免。"},{"pid":"3329391e9031d3f499e178212b516339906a90a2","tid":1496062,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"白痴先理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12688df67451747278ac6d07386aedc447d5ffef","tid":1496062,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"又話唔關租事？最低工資呀嘛，佔路呀嘛？<br />\n做咩要人減租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18fad4d44cf19f24acff8176447ca44a576a456","tid":1496062,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"點解要減呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d82827dc86a91d7b3e369c08ca28cba7db94ea","tid":1496062,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"唔識做生意就唔好做"},{"pid":"b28c77a4257a789da6aee084e5ab2d7815d0b3bc","tid":1496062,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"廢？"},{"pid":"8e3d62f7aaae50edafc453b0340b2116b81cfae4","tid":1496062,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite